	<div class=3D"post-body">
		<!--?xml encoding=3D"utf-8" ?--><p>No matter how often I host Thanksgivin=
g or Friendsgiving, I always second-guess myself: Exactly how much turkey p=
er person should I make? The turkey=E2=80=99s size determines how big a hel=
ping each guest receives=E2=80=94not to mention how much will remain for th=
e coveted leftovers. The number is so specific that I never remember it rig=
ht off the bat. And because the size of the turkey changes depending on the=
 number of guests, I can=E2=80=99t just rely on the bird I used for last ye=
ar=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://www.tasteofhome.com/collection/thanksgiving=
-turkey-recipes/" tabindex=3D"0" aria-label=3D"Thanksgiving turkey recipe" =
data-name=3D"Shop Now" data-module=3D"content engagement" data-position=3D"=
embedded links">Thanksgiving turkey recipe</a>.</p>
<p>Luckily, there=E2=80=99s an easy formula to ensure you=E2=80=99ll create=
 enough food for every guest. To further simplify things, we=E2=80=99ve cre=
ated a guide to help you pick the perfect-sized turkey for your <a href=3D"=
https://www.tasteofhome.com/collection/ultimate-thanksgiving-dinner-menu/" =
tabindex=3D"0" aria-label=3D"Thanksgiving dinner menu" data-name=3D"Shop No=
w" data-module=3D"content engagement" data-position=3D"embedded links">Than=
ksgiving dinner menu</a>. Once decided, there are usually some follow-up qu=
estions, like whether it=E2=80=99s better to buy one huge bird or two small=
 ones, and how to thaw and season your bird. We=E2=80=99ve got you covered =
with those answers, too.</p>
<h2>How much turkey should I buy per person?</h2>
<p></p><figure><img decoding=3D"async" loading=3D"lazy" data-tmbi-lazy=3D"t=
rue" class=3D"alignnone size-large wp-image-2191079" style=3D"aspect-ratio:=
 0.8;" src=3D"https://www.tasteofhome.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/How-Mu=
ch-Turkey-Do-You-Need-Per-Person_Graphic.jpg?fit=3D680%2C995" alt=3D"How Mu=
ch Turkey Do You Need Per Person" width=3D"700" height=3D"1024" data-recalc=
-dims=3D"1"><figcaption>TASTE OF HOME, GETTY IMAGES</figcaption></figure><d=
iv class=3D"ad-container-wrapper dai-ad-wrapper glide-on-mobile"><div id=3D=
"dai-content-1" class=3D"ad" data-ad-slot-name=3D"/article/content_1" data-=
