a-ad-wrapper-classes=3D""></div></div>
<ul>
<li><strong>For large groups:</strong> Prepare your favorite turkey recipe =
and make extra <a href=3D"https://www.tasteofhome.com/recipes/grilled-turke=
y-drumsticks/" tabindex=3D"0" aria-label=3D"grilled turkey legs" data-name=
=3D"Shop Now" data-module=3D"content engagement" data-position=3D"embedded =
links">grilled turkey legs</a> or <a href=3D"https://www.tasteofhome.com/re=
cipes/brined-grilled-turkey-breast/" tabindex=3D"0" aria-label=3D"grilled t=
urkey breast" data-name=3D"Shop Now" data-module=3D"content engagement" dat=
a-position=3D"embedded links">grilled turkey breast</a> on the side. Grilli=
ng frees up the oven to make Thanksgiving sides and keeps clean-up to a min=
imum.</li>
<li><strong>For smaller groups:</strong> Try pairing a <a href=3D"https://w=
ww.tasteofhome.com/article/small-turkey/" tabindex=3D"0" aria-label=3D"smal=
l turkey" data-name=3D"Shop Now" data-module=3D"content engagement" data-po=
sition=3D"embedded links">small turkey</a> with <a href=3D"https://www.tast=
eofhome.com/recipes/slow-cooker-turkey-breast/" tabindex=3D"0" aria-label=
=3D"slow-cooker turkey breast" data-name=3D"Shop Now" data-module=3D"conten=
t engagement" data-position=3D"embedded links">slow-cooker turkey breast</a=
> or slow-cooked <a href=3D"https://www.tasteofhome.com/recipes/turkey-leg-=
pot-roast/" tabindex=3D"0" aria-label=3D"turkey leg pot roast" data-name=3D=
"Shop Now" data-module=3D"content engagement" data-position=3D"embedded lin=
ks">turkey leg pot roast</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p>If your family and friends don=E2=80=99t love turkey, skip the whole bir=
d and just make the white or dark meat. You can augment the meal with <a hr=
ef=3D"https://www.tasteofhome.com/collection/alternative-thanksgiving-main-=
dishes/" tabindex=3D"0" aria-label=3D"alternative Thanksgiving main dishes"=
 data-name=3D"Shop Now" data-module=3D"content engagement" data-position=3D=
"embedded links">alternative Thanksgiving main dishes</a> like vegetarian-f=
riendly <a href=3D"https://www.tasteofhome.com/recipes/roasted-pumpkin-lasa=
gna/" tabindex=3D"0" aria-label=3D"pumpkin lasagna" data-name=3D"Shop Now" =
data-module=3D"content engagement" data-position=3D"embedded links">pumpkin=
 lasagna</a>.</p>
<h2>How many side dishes do I need for Thanksgiving?</h2>
<p>We generally recommend having two to four side dishes, but the total num=
ber depends on your guest list, oven space and family traditions. Try makin=
g three to five of your family=E2=80=99s favorite sides and encouraging gue=
sts to bring their favorite <a href=3D"https://www.tasteofhome.com/collecti=
on/nearly-forgotten-thanksgiving-side-dishes/" tabindex=3D"0" aria-label=3D=
"non-traditional Thanksgiving sides" data-name=3D"Shop Now" data-module=3D"=
content engagement" data-position=3D"embedded links">non-traditional Thanks=
giving sides</a>. Rolls, cranberry sauce and <a href=3D"https://www.tasteof=
home.com/collection/traditional-thanksgiving-dessert-ideas/" tabindex=3D"0"=
 aria-label=3D"Thanksgiving desserts" data-name=3D"Shop Now" data-module=3D=
"content engagement" data-position=3D"embedded links">Thanksgiving desserts=
</a> are easy to outsource.</p>
